{"tid":648072,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"真正鍾意動畫既人先會覺得南極>>>>>>>京紫","createTime":"2018-04-30T11:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T02:39:09.000Z","uid":59491,"like":7,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"06288267e4090fbf4219f9cdc969579eda399ced","tid":648072,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"睇南極你真係會喊到嘩嘩聲<br />\n你唔會知點解佢一集同一個pattern都會睇到咸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nE.g. 睇十一十二集佢一開始都係用啲日常玩玩下嘅劇情<br />\n後半段爆seed展開主線播歌催淚<br />\n<br />\n至於京紫唔係話唔勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢只係作畫較好嘅作品<br />\n睇京紫完全冇個種好神奇既感覺<br />\n就算準備話出個陣都係咁講<br />\n<br />\n所以話南極係一月最佳 京紫最多只係一月第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 下面唔好講銷量 <br />\n先唔講賣到無貨 如果供應量多應該會買到2萬幾3萬<br />\n有啲根本靠買碟抽活動卷呃腐女錢推高銷量"},{"pid":"1249407eab36e04d17339d36d4083ff73b91a2c2","tid":648072,"uid":46933,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦京紫頭4都入唔到啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfee948542457651c58010c393db6f90d2b2cecc","tid":648072,"uid":35667,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"細蚊仔睇唔明京紫先吹奏南極<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed8ce2afd6588919bebad44270314e76e246b2d","tid":648072,"uid":46389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:25:05.000Z","msg":"好悶"},{"pid":"f4ee401a78d61305d76a90ed98a3cc87d7de79f5","tid":648072,"uid":49057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"點樣先為之真正鐘意動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbf48ddaf4f7c1e6b4bc961bf9a8279a1f2d202","tid":648072,"uid":6327,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:48:31.000Z